value.0: This finely-wrought suit of full plate and embroidered surcoat look as if they would cost a fortune to have made, putting it strictly in the realm of noble warriors.
These notorious silks are used by many assasins to carry out dark deeds, though they arern't sold openly, they are known to command exagerating prices on any market!
